---
// About Section
---

<section id="about" class="pt-16 sm:pt-20 lg:pt-24 pb-12 sm:pb-16 lg:pb-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-72 h-72 bg-red-200 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl"></div>
        <img 
          src="/images/about.webp" 
          alt="Traditional Tamil gold jewelry collection" 
          width="5821"
          height="3877"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="relative rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-[250px] sm:h-[350px] lg:h-[450px] object-cover object-center"
          style="object-position: center 45%;"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Content -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Trusted Gold Buyers in <span class="text-red-600">Coimbatore</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          MRG Gold Buyers is a trusted name for people looking to <strong>sell their old gold at the highest market rate</strong> in Coimbatore, Tiruppur, and Theni. With years of experience in gold valuation, we provide transparent testing, instant payment, and hassle-free service.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">We help customers sell:</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Old gold jewellery</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Broken gold ornaments</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Pledged gold</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Second hand gold</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Gold coins and bars</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 font-semibold">
            Our goal is simple: <span class="text-red-700">offer the best price with honest evaluation and instant payment.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            Get Free Valuation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
